node.text:
⚠ New GeForce Garage build ⚠
 
RahulKohli13 stopped by the studio and assembled an awesome ASUS USA x Gundam gaming rig.

Specs:
Chassis: ASUS TUF Gaming GT 301 Zaku II
GPU: ASUS STRIX RTX 3070 Ti
MB: ASUS TUF B550M Zaku II
CPU: Ryzen 7 5800X
Cooler: ASUS TUF Gaming LC 240 RGB Zaku II
Mem: Dominator RGB 32GB 3200Mhz
Storage: Aorus Gen4 1TB + Intel 760p M.2 1TB
Power: SeaSonic Prime 1000W
